window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From USA Today and Amazon Bestselling Author Laura Pavlov, comes a new Small Town, Enemies to Lovers, Standalone Sports Romance in the brand new Magnolia Falls Series.</b></p> <p>Demi Crawford was Magnolia Falls royalty.</p> <p>I was the boxer from the wrong side of the tracks.</p> <p>She was the epitome of everything good, while I was broody and rebellious.</p> <p>We couldn’t be more different.</p> <p>Her family was enemy number one which made her guilty by association.</p> <p><i>I despised her before I even knew her.</i></p> <p>It was easier that way.</p> <p>But now she’d moved in next door to me, and she was everywhere I turned.</p> <p>I couldn’t avoid her no matter how hard I tried.</p> <p>She was beautiful and honest and sweet.</p> <p>Everything I knew I shouldn’t want.</p> <p><i>Shouldn’t need.</i></p> <p>They say there’s a fine line between love and hate—and I don’t know when I crossed over.</p> <p>I was so wrapped up in this girl I couldn’t see straight.</p> <p><i>She was the right hook I never saw coming.</i></p> <p>Hating her was supposed to be my end game.</p> <p>Loving her… well, that was just the beginning.</p> <p>But the secrets that lived between us threatened to tear us apart.</p> <p>Lucky for her—I was a born fighter.</p> <p><i>And she was definitely worth the fight.</i></p>"; 
